data.description: Looking for a diamond in the rough? Looking for a serene, secluded area with lots of land space? Look no further. This 4-bedroom 1.5 bath property sits on a one acre of land in the Woodland Smyrna area. This property comes with 2 fireplaces in both living and sitting rooms. If you like fishing and or crabbing, take a drive just a stone’s throw away and arrive at Woodland Beach, relax, and spend some time with family or friends! You want an open space across from you, this property got you covered with a vast open restricted land across from the property. With vision and elbow grease, you can make this your new home! Come and check it out and buy it before someone else gets it. Investor Alert!! Handyperson Special! Property is in need of some TLC! First time buyer with cash/203k special! Property needs work! Septic will not pass. Currently working. Sellers will not update septic. Property sold "AS IS” Sellers will not make any repairs.
